archimate:BusinessProcess.name: Define Engaged Element Relationships
archimate:BusinessProcess.documentation: Define Engaged Element Relationships process defines the relationship between engaged elements e.g. dependencies between engaged elements.

properties.value: Define Engaged Element Relationships process defines the relationship between engaged elements e.g. dependencies between engaged elements. For example, in the case of a technician visit to a customer premise the expected time of technician arrival may be dependent on, amongst other things, distance from customer premise, level of traffic congestion etc.
